    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years! You might find a tiny sign of use here or there if you look closely, but it runs like a dream and is totally ready for your next big road trip. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm super happy to chat and tell you more!",
