    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride of ownership, offering a perfect balance of performance and comfort. The exterior maintains a brilliant shine, with only minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with careful driving. Inside, you will find a pristine, non-smoker cabin with well-preserved upholstery and high-functioning electronics, including a responsive infotainment system and dual-zone climate control. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it features a comprehensive service history, a smooth-shifting transmission, and a quiet, efficient engine. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change and a thorough multi-point inspection, ensuring the tires and brakes have plenty of life remaining. This is a turn-key vehicle that delivers a solid, quiet ride, making it an ideal choice for anyone looking for a dependable and attractive daily driver.",
