    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been curated to meet our rigorous standards for quality and performance. It exhibits a well-documented maintenance history and remains in commendable aesthetic and mechanical order. This is a premier opportunity to acquire a high-functioning asset that offers a superior driving experience and exceptional long-term value. Available for immediate acquisition.",
