      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a gem to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. It runs like a dream and is ready to head home with you today. Feel free to shout if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
